item.title: CVE-2017-2748|2024-08-05T14:02:07.706Z -- isaac%20mizrahi -- isaac%20mizrahi%20smartwatch%20mobile%20app
item.description: A potential security vulnerability caused by the use of insecure (http) transactions during login has been identified with early versions of the Isaac Mizrahi Smartwatch mobile app. HP has no access to customer data as a result of this issue.
